To run the test:

Go to your project directory from terminal and hit following commands

mvn test (defualt will run on local firefox browser)
mvn test "-Dbrowser=chrome" (to use any other browser)
mvn test "-Dcloud_config=saucelab_windows_chrome52" (to run test on cloud test platforms)



Before the running the test there are some setup should be made:

Download eclipse and import the project
Install Java and set path.
Install Maven and set path.
Download the drivers for various Browsers and set path (chromeDriver, geckodriver)
If you want to run tests in Suace labs in different browsers create a properties file in the cloudBrowserConfigs and fill in the details
For finding the number of emails the method is in the stepDefinitions>UserStepDefintion
All the features will be in the features folder in the Test>Resource